metadata.name: Neo Tokyo By LeBoomington
metadata.description:
Welcome to Neo Tokyo by artist LeBoomington with music by Music Mainnet.

The Citadel Tower shoots a laser into the Moon every time Citizens band together and start a project. So every few seconds.  
This map is a celebration of Neo Tokyo, home of the Metaverse entrepreneurs, quietly building the future. 

Follow the linktree on Twitter and explore LeBoomington's work, discover the Rootz Tribe ecosystem, Caduceus software and learn about Neo Tokyo and Music Mainnet. 

Find the link to the Neo Tokyo Interlinked Map project and explore an interactive representation of the Citadel built using Visual Language of Thought software by Caduceus.
